'''Germanic cognates:''' Old Saxon [[kussian]] (Dutch [[kussen]]), Old High German [[kussen]] (German [[küssen]]), Old Norse [[kyssa]] (Swedish [[kyssa]]), Gothic [[𐌺𐌿𐌺𐌾𐌰𐌽]]

'''Indo-European cognates:''' Greek [[κυνεῖν]]

